title: The High Price of Micro-Fame (My Face on Phil's Wall)
description:
Who's Phil?  This is Phil: https://www.youtube.com/user/philddlesticks/videos
Trust me, I have no delusions as to just how "micro" my "micro-fame" is… but yeah, some days, you wake up and find out that you're on a poster on SOMEBODY'S wall.  Shout out to Phil.  Stay vegan, you fucking degenerate.
